<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-4204612">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Sun, 12/01/2013 - 19:27 | <a href="/news/2013-12-01/bitcoin-plunges-bear-market#comment-4204612" class="active">4204612</a></span>
